PROJECT GOAL: This java Project implements following web rest services

PROJECT PRE-REQ:
        1. JDK 1.8
        2. Eclipse IDE
        3. http-2.2.1.jar
        4. javax.mail.jar
        5. javax ws rs jar
        6. smtp configurations
        
WEB SERVICES:
1. User Registration :
   Ex:
      POST http://localhost:8067/Register
      {"name":"Zeeshan","email":"zeeshan.rizvi010@gmail.com","pincode":"560075"}
      
2. User Email Verification by sending dynamic http link to mail which expires in 15 minutes :
   Ex:
      PUT http://localhost:8067/VerifyEmail
      {"userid":"zeeshan.rizvi010@gmail.com"}
      
3. User Info dump on clicking http link sent to mail:
   Ex:
      GET http://localhost:8067/Login?zeeshan.rizvi010@gmail.com
      
  
